This work is an unofficial, community-built interactive companion for the
concepts taught in Harvard CS249r: Machine Learning Systems. It is based on
the open-source textbook "Machine Learning Systems" by Prof. Vijay Janapa
Reddi et al., available at https://mlsysbook.ai/, which is licensed under
CC BY-NC-SA 4.0.

